TopicTitle: Russian fighter jet and helicopter submissons.

Articles.Content:
Hello, I'd like you ksp fighter jet creators to publish your Russian fighter jets and helicopters.

I was thinking that you could do MIG Jets, SU Series jets, And kamov and mil helicopter series.

The mods  you need to use are Airplane plus, BDarmory, And the dlc.

(You can use those and any other mod you like. Those mods are recommended.)

Good luck!
